类 LaunchableMesosWorker

  • 所有已实现的接口:
    LaunchableTask

    public class LaunchableMesosWorker
extends java.lang.Object
implements LaunchableTask
    Implements the launch of a Mesos worker.

    Translates the abstract ContainerSpecification into a concrete Mesos-specific Protos.TaskInfo.
